Ranger Help for: naturestrike
==============================

SYNTAX:      naturestrike <target>
USAGE:       Wilderness only
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     150
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill is the ultimate melee attack available to Rangers, channeling
the raw power of nature through the Ranger's weapon. Naturestrike deals
the highest melee damage of any Ranger skill, combining physical force
with elemental energy from the surrounding terrain. The Ranger must be
in wilderness terrain to draw upon Gaia's power. The damage type and
visual effect vary by terrain. This skill has a significant cooldown
and SP cost, making it best reserved for the most dangerous foes.
